<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">

</head>
<body>
    <style>
        body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    color: #333;
}

header {
    background-color: #005b96;
    color: white;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

header .logo img {
    max-width: 150px;
}

nav ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
}

nav ul li {
    display: inline;
    margin: 0 15px;
}

nav ul li a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.hero-section {
    background-color: #0096d1;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 20px;
}

.cta-button {
    background-color: #ff6f61;
    color: white;
    padding: 15px 30px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    display: inline-block;
}

.about-section, .services-section, .team-section, .contact-section {
    padding: 60px 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

.service, .team-member {
    margin: 20px 0;
}

footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
}

    </style>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Clinic Logo">
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/signin">Signin</a></li>
                <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="/therapists">Therapists</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="home" class="hero-section">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Occupational Therapy Clinic</h1>
        <p>Helping you live your best life through personalized therapy.</p>
        <a href="/services" class="cta-button">Explore Our Services</a>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="about-section">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>We are dedicated to improving the lives of our patients through expert therapy and personalized care plans.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="services-section">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <div class="service">
            <div class="service-cards"> 
                <img src="fine motors.jpg" alt="">
                <h3>Fine Motor Skills Therapy</h3>
                <p>Enhancing hand-eye coordination. </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service">
                <div class="service-cards"> 
                   <img src="gross motors.jpg" alt="">
                   <h3>Gross Motor Skills Therapy</h3>
                   <p>Improving Balance and coordination.</p>
                </div>
        </div>
            <div class="service-cards">
                 <img src="sensory integration.png" alt="">
                <h3>Sensory Integration</h3>
                <p>Helping Children With Sensory Processing Disorders.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="team" class="team-section">
        <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
        <div class="team-member">
            <img src="/images/therapist1.jpg" alt="Therapist 1">
            <h3>Jane Doe, OTR/L</h3>
            <p>Jane specializes in pediatric therapy with over 10 years of experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
            <img src="/images/therapist2.jpg" alt="Therapist 2">
            <h3>John Smith, OTR/L</h3>
            <p>John is an expert in geriatric therapy and hand rehabilitation.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact-section">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>We'd love to hear from you! Reach out to us with any questions or to schedule an appointment.</p>
        <form action="#" method="POST">
            <label for="name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
            <label for="message">Message</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>
            <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Occupational Therapy Clinic. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>